Project Title: Electronic Medical Record (EMR) System – Wrenwood Community Healthcare

This project is a web-based PHP application designed to manage patient records for a medical practice. It allows users to search for patients, view patient history, and add new patient records and medical events.

The system uses a MySQL database with three main tables:

* Patients
* Procedures
* Patient History

All required functionality has been implemented, including:

* Searching for patients by name
* Viewing patient history by patient ID
* Adding new patients
* Adding new patient history records

Known Issues:

* The patient history search page may produce errors if there is a mismatch between database column names and the PHP code.
* The interface is basic and does not include advanced styling.

Overall, the system meets the project requirements and demonstrates core PHP and MySQL integration.
